# Procurement Rules (V2.1)

**Authority:** `00_architecture_authority.mdc`

## Module layout

| Domain | Module path |
|--------|-------------|
| Vendors, bills, contracts, quotations | `backend/src/modules/vendors/` |
| Project selling, agreements | `backend/src/modules/project-selling/` |
| Contractor billing, retention, FIFO | `modules/vendors/services/` |

## Patterns

- CRUD: `TenantRepository` → service → route → `/api/v1`
- Bill/invoice payments that hit GL: `FinancialPostingService` (via journal posting services)
- Contractor advances: `contractorFifo`, vendor bill advance stack in `modules/vendors/services/`
- Quotation validation: `shared/quotation-validation/` → synced to `backend/src/quotationValidation/`
- Contract retention: `shared/contract-retention/` → `backend/src/contractRetention/`

## Real-time (mandatory)

Emit after every mutation affecting:

- `vendor`, `bill`, `contract`, `quotation`, `purchase_order`
- Contractor billing, retention releases, bill payments

Reference: `modules/vendors/routes/billsRoutes.ts`

## MUST NOT

- New flat `backend/src/services/vendors*.ts` handlers
- SQLite or offline procurement flows
- Duplicate quotation/retention logic outside `shared/`

## Frontend

- API via `services/api/repositories/*Api.ts`
- React Query hooks + socket invalidation for bill/vendor lists
